1-Macaamiilka ayaa dooran kara meesha uu rabo in la geeyo , kadib ayuu arki doona masaafada lagu tagi karo meeshas iyo lacagta lagu geynayo , kadib ayuu dooran karaa nuuca gaari u rabo inuu raaco hadii ay online yihiin kadib waxuu ku xirmi doona darawalka ugu dhaw ee dhaweeye.
2-Dalabkada waxaa arki doono darwalka kuugu dhaw ee nuuca gaari aad dalbatay , isaga ayaaana ku aqbali kara ama ku diidi kara.
3- Dalbadaha ayaa heli doono fariin ku saabsan in la diiday ama in la aqbalay.
4-Darawalka ayaa u dhaqaaqaya dhanka dalbadaha siyuu u raadiyo meesha u ku suganyahy.
5-Dalbadaha ayaa heli doono fariin ah in darwalka usoo socdo dhankiisa.
6-Dalbadaha ayaa heli doono fariin ah in darawalka soo gaaray.
7-Kadib waxaa bilaabanaya safarkii marka uu macaamiilka soo raaco gaariga.
8-Darawalka waxuu arki doona jidka u ku socdo iyo sida ugu dhaw u ka tagi karo meesha u dalbaday macaamiilka.
9-Marki la gaaro meeshi u dalbaday macaamiilka waxay heli doonan labadaba warqad ay ku qoranthay warbixin ku saabsan lacagti safarka.
10-Ugu danbeen labadaba waxay aqbali doonan warqada lacagta , sido kale mid walba kan kale ayuu qiimeen ku samen doona intii ay safarka ku wada jireen.
